# Testing

- Tests must be completely offline -- no real HTTP calls. Mock `http.Client` with `mocktail`.
- Mock services/storage at the boundary, not internal methods. Inject mocks via constructor DI.
- Register fallback values in `setUpAll` for any types used with `any()` matchers.
- Test file naming: `test/<module>_test.dart` mirroring the source file.
- Use `group()` to organize by class or feature, keep test descriptions concise.
- Run `make test` to validate. All tests must pass with zero failures before pushing.
- No widget tests unless explicitly needed -- focus on logic, serialization, and service layers.
